frames.caption: A dramatic scene depicts a ship emerging from a painting, surrounded by swirling clouds. The artwork is framed in an ornate golden frame, creating a surreal blend of art and reality. The ship appears to be sailing through a storm, with clouds spilling into the room.
frames.description: The scene is set in a gallery or museum where a painting of a ship at sea seems to come to life. The ship, caught in a storm, appears to break free from the confines of the frame, with clouds and mist extending into the gallery space.

frames.caption: A dramatic scene depicts a ship navigating through turbulent waters, with waves appearing to spill out of the painting's frame. The ornate golden frame contrasts with the stormy sea and sky, creating a surreal blend of art and reality.
frames.description: The image shows a painting of a ship in a stormy sea, with the waves seemingly extending beyond the frame into the room. This creates an immersive effect, merging the artwork with its surroundings.
